\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2491144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1590276\charrsid1986722 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
