's, I remember him - that section of the family had several funerals and - in my later schooldays and afterwards I attended these funerals and my recollection of that man is a man with a napkin ticked in his collar, glasses on, presiding with a carving kn
ife and fork over a beautiful roast ham. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1590276\charrsid1986722 I don't remember him any other way.
