It's difficult to ex - to explain why I was shocked. I suppose it was something new and something - associated with unpleasantness. As people would said and did say, he looked very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2491144 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1590276\charrsid1986722 Did it tie in with your preconceived notion of death at all?
